114
00:11:51,980 --> 00:11:53,890
You asshole!

115
00:11:53,890 --> 00:11:56,850
You think you can say anything with that mouth of yours?

116
00:11:56,850 --> 00:11:59,380
I'm not a scholar, and I have no dignity.

117
00:11:59,380 --> 00:12:04,160
