236
00:23:54,880 --> 00:23:57,440
All right. Let's eat.

237
00:23:57,440 --> 00:23:59,010
I hope you enjoy it.

238
00:23:59,010 --> 00:24:01,140
Enjoy.

239
00:24:03,480 --> 00:24:06,300
