Dad, you're such a goofball.

251
00:24:49,380 --> 00:24:51,940
No, I'm not a goofball.

252
00:24:51,940 --> 00:24:54,860
I'm a comedian.

253
00:24:56,670 --> 00:24:58,150
 Was I funny? 

254
